WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 19=
=No Breakups Before Dawn=

00:01:01.020 --> 00:01:03.380
(Suga Love)

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:17.080
Mr. Yu,

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:19.800
how's Ding Daang doing now?

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:27.200
Much better.

00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:29.040
She'll be fine after some rest.

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:31.390
Thanks for taking her
to the hospital yesterday.

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:41.600
I heard the test results are here.

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:43.440
Let me take a look.

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:45.200
Sure.

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:53.440
Here you go, Mr. Yu.

00:01:55.500 --> 00:01:59.740
(X-ray Examination Report)

00:02:04.160 --> 00:02:05.720
Can you make me a chestnut cake?

00:02:05.720 --> 00:02:06.760
I'll bring it to her.

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.440
Got it, Mr. Yu. Just a minute.

00:02:11.660 --> 00:02:16.100
(Slight fracture in the lower left tibia,
no displacement)

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:32.040
Mr. Yu, the cake's ready.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:35.480
Do you want coffee with that?

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:37.960
Mr. Yu.

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.720
Thanks.

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:43.080
Here you are.

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.760
Why does Mr. Yu feel...

00:02:57.760 --> 00:02:59.200
kind of weird today?

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:01.840
I think...

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:03.720
he's just hurt by the boss.

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:06.120
Ding Daang is seriously ruthless.

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.440
She can even pull off that pity act.

00:03:11.320 --> 00:03:12.160
Come on, Xiaowen.

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:13.480
Smash it here.

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.520
Smash hard.

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.800
Uh... maybe you should do it.

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:24.640
I can't do it either.

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:26.280
Ding Daang,

00:03:26.310 --> 00:03:27.160
maybe,

00:03:27.160 --> 00:03:28.720
I should just find a makeup artist.

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:29.760
Someone who can fake it.

00:03:30.320 --> 00:03:31.240
No way.

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:33.720
Yu Kun's way too sharp.

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:35.280
We can't give ourselves away.

00:04:16.280 --> 00:04:17.200
What's wrong with you?

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:22.560
I just remembered something

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:24.520
about your family,

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:26.760
about the past,

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:29.040
about you, and about us.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.600
Back then, it was me who let you down.

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:36.600
I'm sorry.

00:04:37.560 --> 00:04:38.400
Ding Daang.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.600
Let's end the contract.

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:44.000
I'll pay back to you

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.600
the money you invested.

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:58.440
(Is that you?)

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.920
(You're really back, aren't you?)

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:16.000
How ridiculous!

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:20.560
What's on your mind?

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.320
You think pretending to sleep

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:25.960
will help you avoid this?

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:28.160
Ding Daang wants you,

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:30.360
not me.

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.280
What gives you that right

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.600
to deserve her love?

00:05:41.080 --> 00:05:42.000
While I...

00:05:45.640 --> 00:05:48.040
only get to live in your shadow.

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:51.320
Chen Aming,

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.200
tell me.

00:05:55.320 --> 00:05:56.240
Say something.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:01.240
Tell me!

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:04.000
You're good at acting all passionate.

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:05.640
Why are you silent now?

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:20.320
If she loves you,

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:23.640
then I'll become you.

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:26.400
You'll never escape from this place.

00:06:30.440 --> 00:06:31.360
You're always

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:34.920
at my command.

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.200
What's wrong?

00:07:15.400 --> 00:07:16.240
Aming?

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:04.080
Chen Aming.

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:21.280
Chen Aming.

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:35.190
♪I've already lost you♪

00:09:35.190 --> 00:09:41.210
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:09:41.790 --> 00:09:45.070
♪Like a sad movie playing out♪

00:09:45.480 --> 00:09:51.010
♪Bound for a tragic ending♪

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.440
Boss.

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:50.440
Are you okay?

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:55.480
Tell me,

00:11:55.680 --> 00:11:56.840
I'm not that coward.

00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:59.400
I'm not that coward.

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:01.120
Boss!

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:03.320
Boss, calm down.

00:12:03.320 --> 00:12:05.000
Boss, Boss!

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:06.000
Boss!

00:12:08.400 --> 00:12:09.680
I'm not Chen Aming.

00:12:09.680 --> 00:12:10.600
I'm not.

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:12.520
I'm not, I'm not.

00:12:18.760 --> 00:12:19.680
You okay?

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:26.280
Looks like we're about to success.

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:29.840
Success? What does that even mean?

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:31.800
You just want him to love you, don't you?

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:33.440
You started all this.

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.000
You made him hurt again and again.

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:37.200
If he'd rather die just to forget you,

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:39.040
why can't you just let him go?

00:12:40.760 --> 00:12:41.720
Enough, Xibei.

00:12:41.720 --> 00:12:42.560
Stop talking.

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:44.320
Shut up. You're her accomplice.

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:45.760
I need him to stay alive.

00:12:48.560 --> 00:12:50.640
His life matters more than anything.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.080
Yeah.

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:54.920
His condition is heading toward

00:12:54.920 --> 00:12:56.080
the last stage we planned for.

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:57.480
(We're almost there.)

00:12:58.280 --> 00:12:59.480
(You're going to be okay.)

00:13:22.980 --> 00:13:27.100
♪Everything in my memories
feels so beautiful♪

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:34.490
♪In every photo,
your smiles are always so bright♪

00:13:36.850 --> 00:13:40.580
♪And there's that little cat
by the window♪

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:41.600
Get out.

00:13:42.640 --> 00:13:43.800
Get out.

00:13:43.800 --> 00:13:45.360
Get out of my mind.

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:46.960
Yu Kun,

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:48.520
you can't escape this.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.280
Shut up.

00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:51.240
You're not me.

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:52.200
I'm stronger than you.

00:13:52.200 --> 00:13:53.120
I'm tougher than you.

00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:54.200
But you hurt more than I do.

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.080
Why?

00:13:55.080 --> 00:13:56.120
Why is it like this?

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:57.160
Because of love.

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.760
It was all a lie.

00:13:58.760 --> 00:13:59.760
They're all liars.

00:13:59.760 --> 00:14:00.760
Yu Kun!

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:02.960
Stop lying to yourself!

00:14:04.270 --> 00:14:08.500
♪Tears always fall for no reason♪

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:11.640
Ding Daang.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:14.120
My brother is dying.

00:14:16.200 --> 00:14:17.120
What did you just say?

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:19.760
What happened to Aming?

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:22.400
You planned all of this.

00:14:24.240 --> 00:14:25.080
Yes.

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.600
Why did you do it?

00:14:28.560 --> 00:14:30.520
Because in his painful memories,

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.680
ninety percent of it is about you.

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:36.560
We'll answer pain with pain,

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:38.720
fight oblivion with memory,

00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.080
and spark a love

00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:45.980
as sweet as sugar
from the illusion of hate.

00:15:11.400 --> 00:15:18.400
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:30.160
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:15:34.610 --> 00:15:36.550
♪They say♪

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:45.340
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:15:45.860 --> 00:15:48.840
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:15:49.060 --> 00:15:55.010
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:15:56.390 --> 00:16:02.150
♪I've already lost you♪

00:16:02.150 --> 00:16:07.630
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:16:07.930 --> 00:16:13.880
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:16:13.880 --> 00:16:18.660
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:23.800
♪The past will always pass♪

00:16:24.130 --> 00:16:31.710
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:16:32.180 --> 00:16:35.430
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:16:35.990 --> 00:16:41.640
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:47.630
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:16:47.630 --> 00:16:53.890
♪But sadly, it's not you♪